comment._content:
The car is probably an English make and of the mid 1930s to immediate pre-war styling. Can't get enough definition to determine much about the 2  trucks but I'd estimate them to be somewhere between late 30s thru to 50s so that gives the earliest this photo could be of mid 1930s.
What memories of driving around country NSW the white paint topped posts and wire mesh fence on the slopeside of the road bring back.
